title: Three Steps Trading FOREX From Beginner to Advanced
description:
What Will I Learn?

Forex terminology: Leverage, Spread, Stop Loss, Take Profit, Ask, Bid...

Technical Patterns like Head & Shoulders, Double Top - Double Bottom, Flags...

The most useful Technical Indicators and Oscilators

Be able to read news from Economic Calendar

Learn our trading Strategy with Harmonic Patterns

Learn how to manage and reduce risk with open trades

Be able to create own trading strategy

Fundamental and Sentiment Analysis

How to use Fibonacci tool and how to combine it with Elliot Waves Analysis

How to setup Pending Orders
